---
import Gallery from "./components/Gallery.astro";
import MoreButton from "./components/MoreButton.astro";
import MoreButtonBig from "./components/MoreButtonBig.astro";
---

<section>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-[900] text-black/80 dark:text-white">About me</h2>
  <div class="container w-full">
    <div>
      <p
        class="font-[400] text-black/70 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-3 text-pretty"
      >
        Hi, I'm Daniel, but you can call me <b class="text-lime-600 dark:text-lime-200">Dani</b>. I started in the world of
        programming more than <b class="text-lime-600 dark:text-lime-200">4 years ago</b>. Throughout my journey, I have created
        various web applications and over time, programming became something
        wonderful for me because it allows me to capture my ideas and share them
        with others.
      </p>
      <p class="font-[400] text-black/70 dark:text-neutral-200 mt-3 text-pretty">
        During this time, <b class="text-lime-600 dark:text-lime-200">I have learned different technologies</b>, but I
        specialize in <b class="text-lime-600 dark:text-lime-200">TypeScript and JavaScript.</b> Here I leave you the
        technologies that I master and a playlist that you might ðŸ’–.
      </p>
      <div class="my-8 h-fit grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <MoreButtonBig
          title="My skills"
          description="watch my skill technologies"
          src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Typescript_logo_2020.svg/1200px-Typescript_logo_2020.svg.png"
          href="/skills"
        />
        <section class="gap-3 w-full sm:w-auto footer-more">
          <MoreButton
            play
            title="Music for programing"
            description="Playlist by me"
            src="/assets/youtube.jpg"
            href="https://music.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5aJwmtVEhsvGpjKwXen-QfFhY29u01o8&si=T2dT75yxLFoxBKW5"
          />
          <MoreButton
            title="Send me a message"
            href="mailto:danielmosvich.dev@gmail.com"
          >
            <svg
              class="text-black/70 dark:text-neutral-200"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="40px"
              height="40px"
              viewBox="0 0 1024 1024"
              ><path
                fill="currentColor"
                d="M128 224v512a64 64 0 0 0 64 64h640a64 64 0 0 0 64-64V224zm0-64h768a64 64 0 0 1 64 64v512a128 128 0 0 1-128 128H192A128 128 0 0 1 64 736V224a64 64 0 0 1 64-64"
              ></path><path
                fill="currentColor"
                d="M904 224L656.512 506.88a192 192 0 0 1-289.024 0L120 224zm-698.944 0l210.56 240.704a128 128 0 0 0 192.704 0L818.944 224z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </MoreButton>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Gallery />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
      gap: 5rem;
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }
  .footer-more {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
  }
  @media (max-width: 430px) {
    .footer-more {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 430px) {
    .footer-more {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
